  <h1>GHC, le Glasgow Haskell Compiler : un guide pratique 2026</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>Par Coldwast</span><span>Mis à jour le 14 juin 2026</span><span>7 min de lecture</span><span class="tag">#haskell</span><span class="tag">#ghc</span><span class="tag">#compiler</span></div>
  <nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>
  <figure>
    <img class="hero" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461749280684-dccba630e2f6?w=1200&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Du code source à l’écran" width="1200" height="420" loading="eager" />
